        <h5><strong>Alvie Estate</strong></h5>
      </div>
      <div class="white-card">
        <p><a href="http://www.alvie-estate.co.uk/" class="green-link", target="blank">Alvie Estate</a> is home to Clan Warfare and the Zip Park, this beautiful estate near Kincraig also offers clay shooting, highland pony trekking and gorge walking.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="green-header">
        <h5><strong>​​​Blair Castle</strong></h5>
      </div>
