        <p><a href="http://www.blair-castle.co.uk/" class="green-link", target="blank">Blair Castle</a> is home to the UK's only private Army. Blair Castle and its garden is a stunning example of Scottish history.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="green-header">
        <h5><strong>​​Cairngorm Reindeer Herd</strong></h5>
      </div>
