        <h5><strong>​​Loch Garten Osprey Centre</strong></h5>
      </div>
      <div class="white-card">
        <p>​<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Loch_Garten" class="green-link", target="blank">Loch Garten</a> is the largest fresh water Highland loch and home to many Osprey and also Capercaillies, Red squirrels, Wood Peckers and many more. The Osprey Centre offer a fantastic facility to spot these rare and beautiful birds. The loch is also a wonderful place to walk and explore for all ages.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="green-header">
        <h5><strong>​​Walking</strong></h5>
      </div>
      <div class="white-card">
        <p>There are endless options for walks across the Cairngorms National Park from low and easy loch walks to extremely strenuous hikes up Munros. A great place to look for and plan the right walk for you is <a href="https://www.walkhighlands.co.uk/" class="green-link", target="blank">Walk Highlands</a>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="green-header">
        <h5><strong>​​​Smarty Art</strong></h5>
      </div>
      <div class="white-card">
        <p>A great wet weather option, this friendly <a href="http://www.smartyart.co.uk/" class="green-link", target="blank">ceramic painting studio</a> conveniently located on the High Street in Grantown-on-Spey provides the opportunity to create your own souvenir of your Cairngorm holiday – or whatever you like! There is a wide selection of white ceramic ware for all ages to paint and enjoy.</p>
      </div>
