        <h5><strong>​​​Laggan Wolftrax</strong></h5>
      </div>
      <div class="white-card">
        <p><a href="https://scotland.forestry.gov.uk/visit/laggan-wolftrax" class="green-link", target="blank">Laggan Wolftrax</a> has over 20 miles of purpose-built mountain bike trails, from easy greens up to extremely tricky blacks. Access trails wind upwards through the forest, rewarding you with stunning views at the top, as well as the fun of the descent! There’s a bike shop for sales and rentals, plus a friendly cafe, as well as hot showers in case you get just too muddy to get back into the car!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="green-header">
        <h5><strong>​​​Highland Horse Fun in Kingussie</strong></h5>
      </div>
      <div class="white-card">
        <p><a href="http://www.highlandhorsefun.com/" class="green-link", target="blank">Highland Horse Fun</a> can organise pony treks of any duration from an hour up to a full day - an inspirational way to see the landscape at a leisurely pace on their lovely Highland ponies. If you are a more experienced rider, hacks are also possible.</p>
